===教育===
清道郡郡內並沒有設立大學，最高僅到[[高級中學|高等學校]]，計有{{Link-ko|清道電子高等學校|청도전자고등학교}}、{{Internal link helper/ko|錦川高等學校|금천고등학교 (경북)}}兩間公立高中及{{link-ko|慕溪高等學校|모계고등학교}}、{{link-ko|伊西高等學校|이서고등학교}}、[[清道高等學校|清道高等學校]]三間私立高中，總共五間。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_05.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=2&p_cate=&rtn_url=/content/01intro/05_05.asp?ct_idx=175|title=고등학교|accessdate=2017-07-17|author=경상북도청도교육지원청|date=|work=www.cheongdo-e.go.kr|publisher=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117203845/http://www.cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_05.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=2&p_cate=&rtn_url=%2Fcontent%2F01intro%2F05_05.asp%3Fct_idx%3D175|dead-url=no}}</ref>

中學校方面，全郡共有7間，其中4間為公立、3間為私立<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_04.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=1&p_cate=&rtn_url=/content/01intro/05_04.asp?ct_idx=174|title=중학교|accessdate=2017-07-17|author=경상북도청도교육지원청|date=|work=www.cheongdo-e.go.kr|publisher=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200809150225/http://cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_04.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=1&p_cate=&rtn_url=%2Fcontent%2F01intro%2F05_04.asp%3Fct_idx%3D174|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而初等學校則有11間。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_03.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=1&p_cate=&rtn_url=/content/01intro/05_03.asp?ct_idx=173|title=초등학교|accessdate=2017-07-17|author=경상북도청도교육지원청|date=2017-03-01|work=www.cheongdo-e.go.kr|publisher=|language=ko|archive-date=2020-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201117203840/http://www.cheongdo-e.go.kr/content/01intro/05_03.asp?proc_type=view&b_num=1&p_cate=&rtn_url=%2Fcontent%2F01intro%2F05_03.asp%3Fct_idx%3D173|dead-url=no}}</ref>
===觀光===

清道最著名的節慶為「清道[[鬥牛|鬥牛]]節」。其鬥牛並非人與牛隻相鬥，而是牛與牛相鬥，在節日期間會在賽場開放[[賭博|賭博]]，為牛隻下注。<ref name="douniu-djyuan">{{cite news|author=姜遠珍|title=韓清道郡鬥牛 觀光熱點|url=http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/12/4/19/n3569202.htm|publisher=大紀元|date=2012-04-19|accessdate=2017-07-16|archive-date=2020-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200507173422/https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/12/4/19/n3569202.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

